# Pomofly - Cursor Rules

## Project
Pomofly is a Pomodoro timer app with task management.

## Tech Stack
- Next.js 14 (App Router, static export)
- React 18, TypeScript 5
- Tailwind CSS 3.4, shadcn/ui
- Firebase (Auth, Firestore)

## Commands
- `yarn dev` - Development
- `yarn build` - Build
- `yarn test` - Tests

## Code Style
- Use TypeScript strict mode
- Use `useCallback` for callbacks
- Use `React.memo` for expensive components
- Always filter Firestore queries by userId
- Add `'use client'` for client components

## Structure
- `src/app/` - Pages (App Router)
- `src/components/` - React components
- `src/components/ui/` - shadcn/ui
- `src/hooks/` - Custom hooks
- `src/lib/` - Firebase, utilities

## Key Files
- `src/hooks/usePomodoro.ts` - Timer logic
- `src/hooks/useTasks.ts` - Task CRUD
- `src/lib/firebase.ts` - Firebase config
- `src/components/PomodoroTimer.tsx` - Main timer

## Issue Tracking
Uses Beads (bd CLI). Run `bd ready` for available work.
